<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-11-07T10:06:20-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-11-07T10:06:20-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-07T10:06:20-05:00</updated><title>零摩托车扩大阵容，着眼于引进新骑手</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;零S电动摩托车&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/RAji0I6QQRuhHcFtKzU-Hu67z-A=/0x0:4674x3116/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/72838364/MY24_S_Action_1.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图像：零&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;YApDEm&quot;>;零摩托车确实倾向于它的&lt;a href= “https://www.forbes.com/sites/hannahelliott/2014/06/24/meet-the-latest-from-the-tesla-of-motorcycles-the-zero-sr-streetfighter/?sh=6d6d96e04394” >;被誉为“摩托车界的特斯拉”。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;t7ii4Q&quot;>;该公司是该国领先的电动摩托车制造商之一，今天宣布推出两款新车型：配备全新电机的 Model S 街头自行车；以及两款新的运动车型：DS 和 DSR 车型。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;6DVbE8&quot;>;这家总部位于加州的公司旨在通过降低价格和性能等准入门槛来吸引新乘客，希望增加愿意花数万美元购买的人数在电池供电的两轮车上。随着过去二十年新摩托车购买量基本上翻了一番，Zero 认为可以通过增加其已经令人印象深刻的摩托车阵容来吸引这些新骑手。 &lt;/p>; &lt;h3 id=&quot;aWwuDK&quot;>;Z...&lt;/h3>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23949263/zero-motorcycles- model-s-ds-dsr-price-specs&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23949263/zero-motorcycles-model-s-ds-dsr-price-specs" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/7/23949263/zero-motorcycles-model-s-ds-dsr-price-specs</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-07T10:00:40-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-07T10:00:40-05:00</updated><title> Epic 诉 Google 的审判可能会归结为简单与复杂</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google Play 徽标内 Epic Games 徽标和 Google 徽标的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https:/